                        "created_at": "1768572178",
                        "id": "18557286301022888",
                        "text": "The Kyoto most people miss out on (& the side of town where you won\u2019t be drowning in crowds!)\n\nWe\u2019ve all seen the crazy surge in Japan travel the past few years, but most people stick to the same things and it\u2019s getting TOO overcrowded. That\u2019s why I was so honored to work with Kyoto\u2019s tourism and showcase some places around the city that actually WANT more tourists to visit\u2026so please add these to your itinerary! \n\n*Ive since been to Japan 7x and will be back again to continue showing the lesser visited places!\n\n\ud83d\udc8e Comment GEMS & I\u2019ll send you my Kyoto map + guide! \n\n#kyoto #japantravel #kyotoguide"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
